OL,3,CGuernsey man animates music video for
OL,4,CWham!'s Last Christmas
OL,6,FA Guernsey man has played a key part
OL,7,Fin this year's Christmas number one by
OL,8,Fanimating its official lyric video.
OL,10,FAdam Le Gallez, 27, animated the video
OL,11,Ffor WHAM's 'Last Christmas' which has
OL,12,Fgarnered around 430,000 views.
OL,14,FAdam grew up in Guernsey attending
OL,15,FCastel Primary School and Les
OL,16,FBeaucamps High before he ventured into
OL,17,Fanimation.
OL,19,FHe's since collaborated with Universal
OL,20,FStudios, Comedy Central, and Youtuber
OL,21,FKSI.
