OL,3,CGuernsey man animates music video for
OL,4,CWham!'s Last Christmas
OL,6,FAdam says his friend from the UK first
OL,7,Ftold him about a job to create
OL,8,Fanimated music videos, explaining:
OL,9,F"They want to remake George Michael's
OL,10,FCareless Whisper in an animated way
OL,11,Ffor their lyric video on their YouTube.
OL,13,F"And so I thought 'Absolutely, who
OL,14,Fdoesn't like the song?'
OL,16,F"They were really pleased with it and
OL,17,Fthen they said in early November that
OL,18,FChristmas is coming up so they wanted
OL,19,Fto do Last Christmas as well."
