OL,4,CWham!'s Last Christmas
OL,6,FGeorge Michael died on Christmas Day
OL,7,Fin 2016 from heart disease. However,
OL,8,Fhis fellow band member, Andrew
OL,9,FRidgely, took a personal interest in
OL,10,Fthe project.
OL,12,FAdam adds: "I wasn't aware he was
OL,13,Finvolved in the project until about
OL,14,Fhalfway through when I had sent off my
OL,15,Finitial portraits of (Andrew).
OL,17,F"He's come back and said 'Looks good,
OL,18,Fbut it would be better if I could look
OL,19,Fless like a pug.'
