OL,6,F"We had to soften all the details, but
OL,7,FI think he was happy in the end."
OL,9,FAdam is now working on projects
OL,10,Fbringing his own creative ideas to
OL,11,Flife when he has spare time.
OL,13,FHe says: "I just wanted to put more
OL,14,Ftime into personal projects because
OL,15,FI'd spent a lot of time on the paid
OL,16,Fwork, so you sort or neglect your own
OL,17,Fcreative process.
OL,19,F"I've just taken a bit of time to put
OL,20,Ftogether a little song and come up
OL,21,Fwith a little character about otters.
